<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

  <head>
    <title>ALTA Home</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.4.0/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.3.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.4.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.2.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script async src="js/content.js"></script>
    <script async src="js/home_header.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/home_header.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/home_content.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/home_footer.css" />
  </head>
    

  <body id="bg">  
  <!--navigation bar-->
    <header class="stick">
        <%= erb :home_header %>
    </header> 
     
    <div id = "wrapper">
      <div id = "page-content-wrapper">

<!--Welcoming Sign up-->
<div class="welcome-row" id="section1">
        <div id="fade-in">
            <!--can be deleted-->
            <div id="welcoming-box">
                <div class="center">
                    <div class="head-box1">RIDE WITH US
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="center">
                  <%if @loggedin %>
                  <div class="head-box2">Tweet to us <a class="twitter" href="https://twitter.com/ise19team29">@ise19team29</a> to get a taxi
                    </div>
                  <% else %>
                   <div class="head-box2">Sign up now via <a class="twitter" href="/login">Twitter</a> for the Greatest DEALS and FREE RIDES
                    </div>
                  <% end %>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
        

<!--Content 1: About Us-->

    <div class="container info1-container" id="section2">
        <div class="bd-row1 info1-row1">
            <div class="bd-column1">
                <div class="info1-box">
                    <div class="info1-title">About Us</div>
                    <div class="info1-vl"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bd-column2">
                <div class="info1-content">
                    We are Alta. We are here to help you get a taxi through Twitter,so you don't need to bother with credit card information.
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>


<!--Content 2: How to use our service-->

    <div class="info2-container container" id="section3">
        <div class="bd-row1">
            <div class="info2-column">
                <div class="info2-box">
                    <div class="info2-title">How to use our <br> services</div>
                        <div class="info2-content">
                            <ol>
                                <li>Login to Twitter,tweet us by using @altataxi,which taxi type you want (S,M or L) and where you want to go.</li>
                                <li>Our employee will reply or dm you for more information about the taxi.</li>
                                <li>Get in the car and relax till you reach your desired destination. Pay the taxi driver with cash or credit card when you reach the destination.</li>
                            </ol> 
                        </div>
                    </div>
            </div>
            <div class="info2-column">
                <img class="info2-img" src="img/info1.jpg">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>


<!--Content 3: How it works-->

    <div class="info3-container container" id="section4">
        <div class="bd-row1">
            <div class="info3-column">
                <img class="info3-img" src="img/info3.jpeg">
            </div>

            <div class="info3-column info3-column2">
                <div class="info3-box">
                    <div class="info3-title">How does it work</div>
                        <div class="info3-content">
                          The employee would see your tweet and he/she would search the nearest taxi near you. If you do not have location service on in twitter, he/she will reply or dm you to ask for your location.
                          Then he/she would tell you about the taxi information(the taxi's plate and contact number). The taxi driver would ask what's your twitter name and you could confirm it by saying it.
                          Pay the driver when you have reached the destination.  
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>


<!--Content 4: Types of taxi-->

    <div class="slideshow-container" id="section5" style="background-color:#FFFFFF; height: 700px;">
        <div class="info4-indicators">
            <span class="info4-indict" onclick="currentSlide(1)">Type S</span> 
            <span class="info4-indict" onclick="currentSlide(2)">Type M</span>
            <span class="info4-indict" onclick="currentSlide(3)">Type L</span>
        <!-- <span class="info4-indict" onclick="currentSlide(4)">Type 4</span> -->
        </div>
        <div class="mySlides">
            <div class="info4-container container">
                <div class="bd-row1">
                    <div class="info4-column">
                        <div class="info4-box">
                            <div class="info4-title">Types of taxi</div>
                            <div class="info4-content1">Small (S) taxi</div>
                            <div class="info4-content2">
                            This is a 1-4 seated taxi.<br>
                            The cheapest taxi type you find here.<br>
                            <br>
                            This would be great for a low budget ride<br>
                            Price range would be vary based on distance but cheapest rate.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info4-column">
                        <img class="info4-img" src="img/info3.jpeg">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mySlides">
            <div class="info4-container container">
                <div class="bd-row1">
                    <div class="info4-column">
                        <div class="info4-box">
                            <div class="info4-title">Types of taxi</div>
                            <div class="info4-content1">Medium (M) taxi</div>
                            <div class="info4-content2">
                            This is a 1-6 seated taxi <br>
                            This would be a great deal if you are going out as a group.<br>
                            Or you went out to shop and want to bring back a giant screen TV.<br>
                            If you a larger person compare to the others<br>
                            This is fine if you want to ride it alone since it would have a larger breathing room.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info4-column">
                        <img class="info4-img" src="img/info3.jpeg">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mySlides">
            <div class="info4-container container">
                <div class="bd-row1">
                    <div class="info4-column">
                        <div class="info4-box">
                            <div class="info4-title">Types of taxi</div>
                            <div class="info4-content1">Luxury (L) taxi</div>
                            <div class="info4-content2">
                            This will be a 1-4 seated taxi. <br>
                            This will be the most expensive taxi in this service.<br>
                            You will get to sleep in the most fashionable way.Used it to snap other how glamorous you are. <br>
                            This service would allow you to use the pillow and the blanket in the taxi.<br>
                            Don't worry about the car since it would be BMW, Lexus, Mercedes etc with professional driver.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info4-column">
                        <img class="info4-img" src="img/info3.jpeg">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>


<!-- Content 5: Customer Reviews-->

