                    <span class="fa fa-star info5-checked"></span>
                    <span class="fa fa-star info5-checked"></span>
                    <span class="fa fa-star info5-checked"></span>
                    <span class="fa fa-star info5-checked"></span>
                </p>
                <p class="info5-date">28/02/2019</p>
                <p class="info5-reviews">
                    This is one of the great services that I have used. Would higly recommend the L type taxi. It is the best when compared to other services.
