                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info5-column">
            <div class="info5-box">
                <div class="info5-cont">
                <p class="info5-name">Simonas
                        <span class="fa fa-star info5-checked"></span>
                        <span class="fa fa-star info5-checked"></span>
                        <span class="fa fa-star info5-checked"></span>
                        <span class="fa fa-star"></span>
                        <span class="fa fa-star"></span>
                        </p>
                    <p class="info5-date">11/03/2019</p>

                    <p class="info5-reviews">
                        There's not much trouble using these services. Just tweeted to ALTA and the employee is fast in replying.
                        The taxis are similar to other services. 3 star.
                        </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    

<!-- Content 6: Contact us and banner -->
    <div class="info6-container" id="section7">        

        <div class="info6-column">
            <div class="info6-box">
                <div class="info6-cont">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>        

        <div class="info6-maincolumn">
            <div class="info6-box">
                <div class="info6-cont">
                    <p class="info6-title">Get in Touch</p>
                    <p class="info6-content1">
                        For any questions or latest news, find us on Twitter, <a href = "https://twitter.com/ise19team29">@ise19team29</a>.
                        </p>
                    <p class="info6-content2">
                        Don't Forget to sign up for deals and offers!
                        </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info6-column">
            <div class="info6-box">
                <div class="info6-cont">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>


    <!--footer-->
    <%= erb :home_footer %>
  </body>
  
</html>
